dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Roger Long. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Lauren Russell.
Nice to meet you, Lauren. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, my policy number is eight three two zero four.
Thank you, Lauren. What is the year, make, and model of the vehicle involved in the incident?
The vehicle is a two zero one eight Ford Fusion.
Great, could you also confirm your date of birth for verification purposes?
My date of birth is March ten, nineteen eighty-five.
Thank you for providing that information, Lauren. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you for your help.
You're welcome, Lauren. Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
